Akhara, Magess of the 10th Element, Daughter of Namyra <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/usortilegewolfsoul.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sortilege Wolfsoul</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Boardfellow</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(6/7/01 7:00:35 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=91.topic&index=114>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http:\\crio.free.fr\sortilege3.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Story         ( and News &amp; Discussion)</span><hr size=1> I'll add two items to the loot : <br>
